#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:2
msgid "Reset and Boot Sequence"
msgstr "复位和启动顺序"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:4
msgid ""
"A device running MicroPython follows a particular boot sequence to start "
"up and initialise itself after a reset."
msgstr "运行 MicroPython 的设备在复位后遵循特定的启动顺序来启动和初始化自身。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:10
msgid "Hard reset"
msgstr "硬复位"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:12
msgid ""
"Booting from hard reset is what happens when a board is first powered up,"
" a cold boot. This is a complete reset of the MCU hardware."
msgstr "从硬复位启动是板子首次通电时发生的情况，即冷启动。这是 MCU 硬件的完全复位。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:15
msgid ""
"The MicroPython port code initialises all essential hardware (including "
"embedded clocks and power regulators, internal serial UART, etc), and "
"then starts the MicroPython environment. Existing :doc:`RTC "
"</library/machine.RTC>` configuration may be retained after a hard reset,"
" but all other hardware state is cleared."
msgstr ""
"MicroPython 移植代码初始化所有基本硬件（包括嵌入式时钟和电源稳压器、内部串行 UART 等），"
"然后启动 MicroPython 环境。现有的 :doc:`RTC </library/machine.RTC>` 配置在硬复位后可能会保留，"
"但所有其他硬件状态都会被清除。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:21
msgid ""
"The same hard reset boot sequence can be triggered by a number of events "
"such as:"
msgstr "相同的硬复位启动顺序可以由多种事件触发，例如："

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:23
msgid "Python code executing :func:`machine.reset()`."
msgstr "Python 代码执行 :func:`machine.reset()`。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:24
msgid "User presses a physical Reset button on the board (where applicable)."
msgstr "用户按下板上的物理复位按钮（如适用）。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:25
msgid "Waking from deep sleep (on most ports)."
msgstr "从深度睡眠唤醒（在大多数移植版本上）。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:26
msgid "MCU hardware watchdog reset."
msgstr "MCU 硬件看门狗复位。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:27
msgid "MCU hardware brown out detector."
msgstr "MCU 硬件欠压检测器。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:29
msgid ""
"The details of hardware-specific reset triggers depend on the port and "
"associated hardware. The :func:`machine.reset_cause()` function can be "
"used to further determine the cause of a reset."
msgstr "硬件特定复位触发器的详细信息取决于移植版本和相关硬件。:func:`machine.reset_cause()` 函数可用于进一步确定复位的原因。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:36
msgid "Soft Reset"
msgstr "软复位"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:38
msgid ""
"When MicroPython is already running, it's possible to trigger a soft "
"reset by :ref:`typing Ctrl-D in the REPL <repl_soft_reset>` or executing "
":func:`machine.soft_reset()`."
msgstr "当 MicroPython 已经在运行时，可以通过 :ref:`typing Ctrl-D in the REPL <repl_soft_reset>` 或执行 :func:`machine.soft_reset()` 来触发软复位。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:42
msgid ""
"A soft reset clears the Python interpreter, frees all Python memory, and "
"starts the MicroPython environment again."
msgstr "软复位会清除 Python 解释器，释放所有 Python 内存，并重新启动 MicroPython 环境。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:45
msgid "State which is cleared by a soft reset includes:"
msgstr "软复位会清除的状态包括："

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:47
msgid "All Python variables, objects, imported modules, etc."
msgstr "所有 Python 变量、对象、导入的模块等。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:48
msgid ""
"Most peripherals configured using the :doc:`machine module "
"</library/machine>`. There are very limited exceptions, for example "
":doc:`machine.Pin </library/machine.Pin>` modes (i.e. if a pin is input "
"or output, high or low) are not reset on most ports. More advanced "
"configuration such as :func:`Pin.irq()` is always reset."
msgstr ""
"使用 :doc:`machine module </library/machine>` 配置的大多数外设。有非常有限的例外，例如 "
":doc:`machine.Pin </library/machine.Pin>` "
"模式（即引脚是输入还是输出，高还是低）在大多数移植版本上不会被复位。更高级的配置如 :func:`Pin.irq()` 总是会被复位。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:53
msgid "Bluetooth."
msgstr "蓝牙。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:54
msgid ""
"Network sockets. Open TCP sockets are closed cleanly with respect to the "
"other party."
msgstr "网络套接字。打开的 TCP 套接字会相对于对方进行干净地关闭。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:55
msgid "Open files. The filesystem is left in a valid state."
msgstr "打开的文件。文件系统会保持在有效状态。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:57
msgid "Some system state remains the same after a soft reset, including:"
msgstr "软复位后一些系统状态保持不变，包括："

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:59
msgid ""
"Any existing network connections (Ethernet, Wi-Fi, etc) remain active at "
"the IP Network layer. Querying the :doc:`network interface from code "
"</library/network>` may indicate the network interface is still active "
"with a configured IP address, etc."
msgstr "任何现有的网络连接（以太网、Wi-Fi 等）在 IP 网络层保持活动。从代码中查询 :doc:`network interface from code </library/network>` 可能会显示网络接口仍然处于活动状态并具有已配置的 IP 地址等。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:63
msgid ""
"An active :doc:`REPL <repl>` appears continuous before and after soft "
"reset, except in some unusual cases:"
msgstr "活动的 :doc:`REPL <repl>` 在软复位前后看起来是连续的，除了一些特殊情况："

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:66
msgid ""
"A serial UART REPL will restore its default hardware configuration (baud "
"rate, etc)."
msgstr "串行 UART REPL 将恢复其默认硬件配置（波特率等）。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:69
msgid "CPU clock speed is usually not changed by a soft reset."
msgstr "CPU 时钟速度通常不会因软复位而改变。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:70
msgid ""
":doc:`RTC </library/machine.RTC>` configuration (i.e. setting of the "
"current time) is not changed by soft reset."
msgstr ":doc:`RTC </library/machine.RTC>` 配置（即当前时间设置）不会因软复位而改变。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:76
msgid "Boot Sequence"
msgstr "启动顺序"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:78
msgid ""
"When MicroPython boots following either a hard or soft reset, it follows "
"this boot sequence in order:"
msgstr "当 MicroPython 在硬复位或软复位后启动时，它按以下顺序执行启动序列："

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:82
msgid "_boot.py"
msgstr "_boot.py"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:84
msgid ""
"This is an internal script :doc:`frozen into the MicroPython firmware "
"<manifest>`. It is provided by MicroPython on many ports to do essential "
"initialisation."
msgstr "这是一个 :doc:`frozen into the MicroPython firmware <manifest>` 中的内部脚本。它由 MicroPython 在许多移植版本上提供，用于执行基本初始化。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:88
msgid ""
"For example, on most ports ``_boot.py`` will detect the first boot of a "
"new device and format the :doc:`internal flash filesystem <filesystem>` "
"ready for use."
msgstr "例如，在大多数移植版本上 ``_boot.py`` 将检测新设备的首次启动并格式化 :doc:`internal flash filesystem <filesystem>` 以供使用。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:92
msgid ""
"Unless you're creating a custom MicroPython build or adding a new port "
"then you probably don't need to worry about ``_boot.py``. It's best not "
"to change the contents unless you really know what you're doing."
msgstr "除非您正在创建自定义 MicroPython 构建或添加新的移植版本，否则您可能不需要担心 ``_boot.py``。最好不要更改其内容，除非您确实知道自己在做什么。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:99
msgid "boot.py"
msgstr "boot.py"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:101
msgid ""
"A file named ``boot.py`` can be copied to the board's internal "
":ref:`filesystem <filesystem>` using :doc:`mpremote <mpremote>`."
msgstr "可以使用 :doc:`mpremote <mpremote>` 将名为 ``boot.py`` 的文件复制到板的内部 :ref:`filesystem <filesystem>`。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:104
msgid ""
"If ``boot.py`` is found then it is executed. You can add code in "
"``boot.py`` to perform custom one-off initialisation (for example, to "
"configure the board's hardware)."
msgstr "如果找到 ``boot.py``，则会执行它。您可以在 ``boot.py`` 中添加代码来执行自定义的一次性初始化（例如，配置板的硬件）。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:108
msgid ""
"A common practice is to configure a board's network connection in "
"``boot.py`` so that it's always available after reset for use with the "
":doc:`REPL <repl>`, :doc:`mpremote <mpremote>`, etc."
msgstr "一种常见做法是在 ``boot.py`` 中配置板的网络连接，以便在复位后始终可用于 :doc:`REPL <repl>`、:doc:`mpremote <mpremote>` 等。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:112
msgid "boot.py should always exit and not run indefinitely."
msgstr "boot.py 应始终退出，不应无限期运行。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:114
msgid ""
"Depending on the port, some hardware initialisation is delayed until "
"after ``boot.py`` exits. This includes initialising USB on the stm32 "
"port. On these ports, output printed from ``boot.py`` may not be visible "
"on the built-in USB serial port until after ``boot.py`` finishes running."
msgstr ""
"根据移植版本的不同，某些硬件初始化会延迟到 ``boot.py`` 退出之后。"
"这包括在 stm32 移植版本上初始化 USB。在这些移植版本上，从 ``boot.py`` 打印的输出可能在 ``boot.py`` 运行完成之前不会在内置 USB 串行端口上可见。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:119
msgid ""
"The purpose of this late initialisation is so that it's possible to pre-"
"configure particular hardware in ``boot.py``, and then have it start with"
" the correct configuration."
msgstr "这种延迟初始化的目的是可以在 ``boot.py`` 中预配置特定硬件，然后让它以正确的配置启动。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:123
msgid ""
"It is sometimes simpler to not have a ``boot.py`` file and place any "
"initialisation code at the top of ``main.py`` instead."
msgstr "有时不使用 ``boot.py`` 文件而是将任何初始化代码放在 ``main.py`` 的顶部会更简单。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:129
msgid "main.py"
msgstr "main.py"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:131
msgid ""
"Similar to ``boot.py``, a file named ``main.py`` can be copied to the "
"board's internal :ref:`filesystem <filesystem>`. If found then it is "
"executed next in the startup process."
msgstr "与 ``boot.py`` 类似，可以将名为 ``main.py`` 的文件复制到板的内部 :ref:`filesystem <filesystem>`。如果找到，则在启动过程中接下来执行。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:135
msgid ""
"``main.py`` is for any Python code that you want to run each time your "
"device starts."
msgstr "``main.py`` 用于您希望每次设备启动时运行的任何 Python 代码。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:138
msgid "Some tips for ``main.py`` usage:"
msgstr "``main.py`` 使用的一些提示："

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:140
msgid ""
"``main.py`` doesn't have to exit, feel free to put an infinite ``while "
"True`` loop in there."
msgstr "``main.py`` 不必退出，可以在其中放置一个无限的 ``while True`` 循环。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:142
msgid ""
"For complex Python applications then you don't need to put all your code "
"in ``main.py``. ``main.py`` can be a simple entry point that imports your"
" application and starts execution::"
msgstr "对于复杂的 Python 应用程序，您不需要将所有代码放在 ``main.py`` 中。``main.py`` 可以是一个简单的入口点，导入您的应用程序并开始执行::"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:149
msgid ""
"This can help keep the structure of your application clear. It also makes"
" it easy to install multiple applications on a board and switch among "
"them."
msgstr "这有助于保持应用程序结构清晰。它还便于在板上安装多个应用程序并在它们之间切换。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:151
msgid ""
"It's good practice when writing robust apps to wrap code in ``main.py`` "
"with an exception handler to take appropriate action if the code crashes."
" For example::"
msgstr "编写健壮的应用程序时，在 ``main.py`` 中使用异常处理程序包装代码是一种好习惯，以便在代码崩溃时采取适当的操作。例如::"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:168
msgid ""
"Otherwise MicroPython will drop to the REPL following any crash or if "
"main exits (see below)."
msgstr "否则，MicroPython 将在任何崩溃或 main 退出后进入 REPL（见下文）。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:171
msgid ""
"Any global variables that were set in ``boot.py`` will still be set in "
"the global context of ``main.py``."
msgstr "在 ``boot.py`` 中设置的任何全局变量在 ``main.py`` 的全局上下文中仍然有效。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:174
msgid ""
"To fully optimise flash usage and memory consumption, you can copy :doc"
":`pre-compiled <mpyfiles>` ``main.mpy`` and/or ``boot.mpy`` files to the "
"filesystem, or even :doc:`freeze <manifest>` them into the firmware build"
" instead."
msgstr "要完全优化闪存使用和内存消耗，您可以将 :doc:`pre-compiled <mpyfiles>` ``main.mpy`` 和/或 ``boot.mpy`` 文件复制到文件系统，甚至将它们 :doc:`freeze <manifest>` 到固件构建中。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:178
msgid ""
"``main.py`` execution is skipped when a soft reset is initiated from "
":ref:`raw REPL mode <raw_repl>` (for example, when :doc:`mpremote "
"<mpremote>` or another program is interacting directly with MicroPython)."
msgstr "当从 :ref:`raw REPL mode <raw_repl>` 发起软复位时，``main.py`` 的执行将被跳过（例如，当 :doc:`mpremote <mpremote>` 或另一个程序直接与 MicroPython 交互时）。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:183
msgid "Interactive Interpreter (REPL)"
msgstr "交互式解释器（REPL）"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:185
msgid ""
"If ``main.py`` is not found, or if ``main.py`` exits, then :doc:`repl` "
"will start immediately."
msgstr "如果未找到 ``main.py``，或者 ``main.py`` 退出，则 :doc:`repl` 将立即启动。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:188
msgid ""
"Even if ``main.py`` contains an infinite loop, typing Ctrl-C on the REPL "
"serial port will inject a `KeyboardInterrupt`. If no exception handler "
"catches it then ``main.py`` will exit and the REPL will start."
msgstr "即使 ``main.py`` 包含无限循环，在 REPL 串行端口上输入 Ctrl-C 也会注入 `KeyboardInterrupt`。如果没有异常处理程序捕获它，则 ``main.py`` 将退出并启动 REPL。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:192
msgid ""
"Any global variables that were set in ``boot.py`` and ``main.py`` will "
"still be set in the global context of the REPL."
msgstr "在 ``boot.py`` 和 ``main.py`` 中设置的任何全局变量在 REPL 的全局上下文中仍然有效。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:195
msgid ""
"The REPL continues executing until Python code triggers a hard or soft "
"reset."
msgstr "REPL 将继续执行，直到 Python 代码触发硬复位或软复位。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:200
msgid "Soft Bricking (failure to boot)"
msgstr "软变砖（启动失败）"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:202
msgid ""
"It is rare but possible for MicroPython to become unresponsive during "
"startup, a state sometimes called \"soft bricked\". For example:"
msgstr "MicroPython 在启动过程中变得无响应是罕见但可能的情况，这种状态有时被称为“软变砖”。例如："

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:205
msgid ""
"If ``boot.py`` execution gets stuck and the native USB serial port never "
"initialises."
msgstr "如果 ``boot.py`` 执行卡住，原生 USB 串行端口永远无法初始化。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:207
msgid "If Python code reconfigures the REPL interface, making it inaccessible."
msgstr "如果 Python 代码重新配置了 REPL 接口，使其无法访问。"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:209
msgid "Rest assured, recovery is possible!"
msgstr "请放心，恢复是可能的！"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:212
msgid "KeyboardInterrupt"
msgstr "KeyboardInterrupt"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:214
msgid ""
"In many cases, opening the REPL serial port and typing ``Ctrl-C`` will "
"inject `KeyboardInterrupt` and may cause the running script to exit and a"
" REPL to start. From the REPL, you can use :func:`os.remove()` to remove "
"the misbehaving Python file::"
msgstr "在许多情况下，打开 REPL 串行端口并输入 ``Ctrl-C`` 将注入 `KeyboardInterrupt`，可能导致正在运行的脚本退出并启动 REPL。在 REPL 中，您可以使用 :func:`os.remove()` 删除有问题的 Python 文件::"

#: ../../reference/reset_boot.rst:222
msgid "To confirm which files are still present in the internal filesystem::"
msgstr "确认内部文件系统中仍存在哪些文件::"

